ENTRIES1.title: Putts N Pars Family Fun Zone
ENTRIES1.subtitle: Come enjoy various activities with the LPGA-USGA Girls Golf Program, Dave & Buster’s Fun Patrol, Bonita’s Beads, and a tournament long Scavenger Hunt!

ENTRIES1.title: Marathon Gas Station
ENTRIES1.subtitle: Visit the Marathon Station which is located between holes 1 and 10 and enjoy some exciting activities.

ENTRIES1.title: Hole 14
ENTRIES1.subtitle: Enjoy the beautiful views of Hole 14 at the Labatt Party Deck, Chamber Canteen, and Public Bleachers!

ENTRIES1.title: College Day
ENTRIES1.subtitle: Free admission and parking with valid student ID.

ENTRIES1.title: Aon Risk Reward Challenge
ENTRIES1.subtitle: Season-long Aon Risk Reward Challenge will highlight the world’s best professional golfers
